OL,6,FCampaigners in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fsay they're frustrated no money was
OL,8,Fallocated for the A75 in the UK
OL,9,FGovernment's spending review.
OL,11,FThe UK Government and the Scottish
OL,12,FGovernment are working on a
OL,13,Ffeasibility study. However, Springholm
OL,14,Fand Crocketford residents feel the UK
OL,15,FGovernment's spending review was an
OL,16,Fopportunity to commit project funding.
OL,18,FDorothy King, from Springholm, says
OL,19,Fpeople are "constantly on edge" living
OL,20,Fnext to A75 road.
