OL,6,FShe said: "It can be very stressful.
OL,7,FIt affects one's ability to come out
OL,8,Fand enjoy the atmosphere of the
OL,9,Fvillage, to walk along the pavement in
OL,10,Fa safe way and you're constantly on
OL,11,Fedge feeling that at any given time,
OL,12,Fan accident could occur.
OL,14,F"The solution is that the gold
OL,15,Fstandard would be the 20mph limit
OL,16,Fwhich is being rolled in many
OL,17,Fvillages. You're never quite safe here
OL,18,Fand anyone who believes they are,
OL,19,Fthey're dreaming."
