OL,6,F"They still haven't spoken of any
OL,7,Fcapital allocation for a bypass."
OL,9,FYesterday Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,10,Fsaid the Spending Review delivers a
OL,11,Frecord settlement for the Scottish
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FToday Scottish Secretary Ian Murray
OL,15,Fsaid: "The Spending Review shows
OL,16,FScotland is at the heart of the UK
OL,17,Fgovernment's plan for change, helping
OL,18,Fto usher in an industrial
OL,19,Ftransformation across the country."
